channel.title: Pest control
channel.description:
Hello, i have putted pest control in my server and i cant play it, my screen is freezing when i want to log in and when i run my server i got this thing
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "4 32 2646 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:2112) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:25) at server.main(server.java:54) Starting JefkeScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 [/code]
the person who can help me will get rep +++

item.title: Pest control
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

No, that’s thrown because you’re trying to basically ‘convert’ a String containing “4
32 2646 " to an integer, by invoking Integer.parseInt(String). Integers cannot contain spaces, so where you’re invoking it, delete all of the spaces from the String by String.replaceAll(” ", “”);
